{"tid":2103243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【整合】【初選懶人包+QNA】銀髮族冇電話都可以投","createTime":"2020-07-11T05:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T09:55:22.000Z","uid":24331,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"977b2a9b3b727944b3e784bc749d4eaf9572972a","tid":2103243,"uid":24331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:14:56.000Z","msg":"1. 邊度搵到票站？<br />\n<a href=\"https://legco2020.vote4.hk/primaries/stations/HKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.vote4.hk%2Fprimaries%2Fstations%2FHKI&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=3efe34d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legco2020.vote4.hk/primaries/stations/HKI</a><br />\n你選區 (港島/九東/九西/新東/新西) 入面所有票站都去得<br />\n<br />\n2. 我要帶啲咩去投票？<br />\n(1) 身份證 + (2) 住址證明 - 包括水電煤電話單、銀行信、住戶證等等 (文本、電子版本、截圖 及相片皆接納)<br />\n選民登記網站 Cap Screen唔用得<br />\n<br />\n3. 投票過程係點？<br />\n1) Scan 票站既QR CODE<br />\n2) IOS 直接用網站投票 Android好似要down app (聽現場票站義工講既)<br />\n3) 入返票站嘅四位數編號<br />\n4) 係咪傳統界別嘅選民 (e.g. 鄉議局/漁農界/保險界/航運交通界/教育界/法律界/會計界/醫學界/衞生服務界/工程界/建築、測量 、都巿規劃及園境界/勞工界/社會福利界/地產及建造界/旅遊界/商界 /工業界/金融界/金融服務界/體育、演藝、文化及出版界/進出口界 /紡織及製衣界 /批發及零售界 /資訊科技界 /飲食界 <br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">係以上界別嘅選民就撳是 只要你要投超級區議會或者唔係以上界別就撳否</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxDbjYO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxDbjYO.jpg&h=689cc78e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5) 填返身份證號碼 出生日期同埋身份證簽發日期等資料<br />\n6) 選擇你心儀嘅代議士<br />\n7) 拎住網站嘅QR CODE進入票站比職員scan 同埋出示返身份證同埋住址證明文件就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n4. 唔小心撳左是 冇得投超級區議會咁點算？<br />\n重新scan過個QR CODE重新做多次以上流程就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n5. 銀髮族冇電話可唔可以投票<br />\n票站內嘅義工好似會有電話幫啲銀髮族投票<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">多謝各位巴打嘅資料 如果大家喺票站見到啲銀髮族阿叔師奶唔識嘅麻煩過去幫下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為好多票站義工都柒下柒下咁 有錯請更正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8a0f690d416fd4d22558827e419f83ea0cc2a6e7","tid":2103243,"uid":24331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:16:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d2e4756acd401f379e482685626dea981ed91436","tid":2103243,"uid":24331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:18:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28563f10f310862a7108aa9776daa1d27bfa9883","tid":2103243,"uid":24331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:20:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec88d16df089f29f97fd03cc0c9247faadb654f8","tid":2103243,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:21:22.000Z","msg":"我想問多數都按否？"},{"pid":"cdd8771183ed22d221679671c2a648cdb8e82a3a","tid":2103243,"uid":24331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec88d16df089f29f97fd03cc0c9247faadb654f8","tid":2103243,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:21:22.000Z","msg":"我想問多數都按否？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"正常係 因為大多數人都冇申請做傳統功能界別嘅選民"},{"pid":"c7872d51ff1c1181547b452599ee279e6c71bf26","tid":2103243,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc2cfa4220b56e40c6238e180f1b4a637114145","tid":2103243,"uid":55317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:23:59.000Z","msg":"杏花邨係咪冇票站<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d1e3c5d3b4d6dc73b6563f0ceff1b406301fdd","tid":2103243,"uid":19617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T05:25:36.000Z","msg":"帶呢張得唔得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yz51Hh6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYz51Hh6.png&h=6dcf7963&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cfc2c94aa21658cfa2c07fb59cedcfec8301410","tid":2103243,"uid":140984,"like"